OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777460573
OL,3,CTeenager arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man stabbed in Redditch
OL,5,Cunderpass
OL,7,FA 17-year-old boy has been arrested
OL,8,Fafter a man was stabbed in an
OL,9,Funderpass in Redditch in
OL,10,FWorcestershire.
OL,12,FPolice were called to Martley Close
OL,13,Fshortly after 8:35am on Tuesday (28
OL,14,FApril), where they found a 41-year-old
OL,15,Fman with a life-threatening stab wound.
OL,17,FHe died in hospital a short time later.
OL,19,FThe teenager has been arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,21,Fpolice custody.
