OL,3,CTeenager arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man stabbed in Redditch
OL,5,Cunderpass
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Gareth
OL,8,FLougher from the Major Investigations
OL,9,FUnit at West Mercia Police said:
OL,11,F"We don't underestimate the concern an
OL,12,Fincident of this nature will raise
OL,13,Fwithin the community, and we are
OL,14,Fgrateful for the support following our
OL,15,Frecent appeal for information.
OL,17,F"We continue to express our
OL,18,Fcondolences to the family of the man
OL,19,Fwho sadly lost his life.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
